  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><img src="/media/13081636/rs4784_wintersport-saalbach-hinterglemm-by-bause-print-090.jpg" alt="Mountain Bar 4" width="868" height="416" rel="868,416" /></p>
<p>The art of après ski remains a real cornerstone of the ski holiday and for many it's as important an element of the trip as the skiing itself.</p>
<p>For those that don't know, Après ski in French means 'after ski', and therefore what you do after skiing which has internationally become the meaning for an after ski drink. </p>
<p>Many alpine resorts and venues offer Après ski in some form! From huge discos, the quiet local or dinner and drinks.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/1e6f5e817a4f4af3b851984b9c3fa71c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1e6f5e817a4f4af3b851984b9c3fa71c}" class="c-btn">View ski holiday deals</a></p>
<div class="data-grid"></div>
<div>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Where to Après Ski</h2>
<p>We have put together a quick overview to make it easier for you to find your perfect Après skiing and snowboarding holiday:</p>
<div class="col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064" href="/{localLink:umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064}" title="Switzerland">Switzerland</a></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13063840/switzerland_graubuenden-ski-region_davos_jakobshorn-bergrestaurant-après-ski.jpg" alt="davosswis" data-udi="umb://media/b74d77b93f684d60abb6afefd6d65a53" /></p>
<ul>
<li>Visit <a data-udi="umb://document/cc17fe79ccd1491a92608658d3af9d55" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc17fe79ccd1491a92608658d3af9d55}" title="St. Moritz">St Mortiz</a> for Après ski extravagance, with even a cocktail named after it</li>
<li>The resort of <a data-udi="umb://document/a95de5322c984f85bcf0f013c457e8df" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a95de5322c984f85bcf0f013c457e8df}" title="Davos">Davos</a> is known to keep the drinks flowing</li>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/4abc3d9367fc4903a52b296414b05ef1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4abc3d9367fc4903a52b296414b05ef1}" title="Zermatt">Zermatt</a> is the place to be for vodka shots and local music</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064" href="/{localLink:umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064}" title="Switzerland" class="c-btn">View Switzerland</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5}" title="France">France</a></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13070900/best-apres-ski-resorts-inghams-holidays-val-disere.jpg" alt="franceapres" data-udi="umb://media/47a54bef283b43e785bde9dee2bf519f" /></p>
<ul>
<li>You can't beat <a data-udi="umb://document/16c56b283bca4ae2b2ada820a5d3a03d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/16c56b283bca4ae2b2ada820a5d3a03d}" title="Val d'Isere">Val d'lsere</a> for parties - especially the famous <strong>La Folie Douce</strong></li>
<li><a style="font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;" data-udi="umb://document/50690c0f70c74050930d18799cab6fa8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/50690c0f70c74050930d18799cab6fa8}" title="Val Thorens">Val Thorens </a>offers underground nightclubs so you can party until the early hours</li>
<li>For a vibrant town centre with lots of options, it's worth visiting <a data-udi="umb://document/870730cefeb2441dab9ccfec19c2fe88" href="/{localLink:umb://document/870730cefeb2441dab9ccfec19c2fe88}" title="Meribel">Meribel</a></li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5}" title="France" class="c-btn">View France</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902" href="/{localLink:umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902}" title="Italy">Italy</a></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13083850/monte-seura-67.jpg" alt="selvaita" data-udi="umb://media/ba832f5893544447b33bfe33036e4dfd" /></p>
<ul>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/37d9070a8d4e4a609b9c192e453f0f97" href="/{localLink:umb://document/37d9070a8d4e4a609b9c192e453f0f97}" title="Selva">Selva</a> offers plenty of bars with snowy scenery outside and games &amp; entertainment inside</li>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/2dcb1a3292da421780aa165d449493a9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2dcb1a3292da421780aa165d449493a9}" title="Cortina D’Ampezzo">Cortina</a> offers the luxury version of Après ski with jazz and cocktail bars</li>
<li>A great place to enjoy wine by the fire or out on a terrace would be <a data-udi="umb://document/a0b1d3c577424320a9af2e1af08b6887" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a0b1d3c577424320a9af2e1af08b6887}" title="Sauze d'Oulx">Sauze d'Oulx</a></li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902" href="/{localLink:umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902}" title="Italy" class="c-btn">View Italy</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb}" title="Austria">Austria</a><span style="color: #202124; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;"></span></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13084973/ischgl-apres_ski.jpg" alt="ischglaus" data-udi="umb://media/70bdfb12289549be8a56892f0b434e8c" /></p>
<ul>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/eb8a4e065fbc4a0fa6a0e0e273886855" href="/{localLink:umb://document/eb8a4e065fbc4a0fa6a0e0e273886855}" title="St Anton">St Anton</a> is famous for its <strong>Mooserwirt</strong> bar which has been going since 1989</li>
<li>Bar hopping and following the crowd is popular in the resort of <a data-udi="umb://document/3c3783ff0696436cb752c8195e705dec" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3c3783ff0696436cb752c8195e705dec}" title="Ischgl">Ischgl</a></li>
<li>If you want to change it up, then head to <a data-udi="umb://document/c0c1aff3b3b645fbaf04f9ae393281d6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c0c1aff3b3b645fbaf04f9ae393281d6}" title="Lech">Lech</a> for the sound of popping champagne corks</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb}" title="Austria" class="c-btn">View Austria</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div class="col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/e8889d8c0e844cde8208727a22b5dfd3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e8889d8c0e844cde8208727a22b5dfd3}" title="Canada">Canada</a></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13092789/whistler-346x200.jpg" alt="WhistlerCanada" data-udi="umb://media/e07805b857db4e9f973bf52f0d85858d" /></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Dusty's Bar</strong> in <a data-udi="umb://document/0c45d07f55a64313a6e4bc714b58b52d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0c45d07f55a64313a6e4bc714b58b52d}" title="Whistler">Whistler</a> in famous to the locals and tourists alike for some afternoon fun</li>
<li><strong>Bar Café d'Epoque</strong> in <a data-udi="umb://document/cc094a7f49b04e9a845adc78e3c77f10" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc094a7f49b04e9a845adc78e3c77f10}" title="Mont Tremblant">Mont Tremblant</a> is a busy nightclub with trendy cocktails</li>
<li>Voted the best bar in Northern Amercia 10 years running, <strong>Le P'tit Caribou</strong> in Mont Tremblant is a must</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/e8889d8c0e844cde8208727a22b5dfd3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e8889d8c0e844cde8208727a22b5dfd3}" title="Canada" class="c-btn">View Canada</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/043e5aa9497c411db243e21ed0a5049b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/043e5aa9497c411db243e21ed0a5049b}" title="Andorra">Andorra</a><span style="color: #202124; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;"></span></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13093200/grandvalira-sign-grandvalira-resorts-image.jpg" alt="AndorraApresSki" data-udi="umb://media/18aee830f51f459f822102fac6d9b7b1" /></p>
<ul>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/e86e0f4a587e4cd8be3c24d7da459a59" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e86e0f4a587e4cd8be3c24d7da459a59}" title="Pas de la Casa">Pas de la casa</a> is home to <strong>Coll Blanc</strong>, a panoramic viewing hot-spot with DJ's from 4pm</li>
<li>The <strong>Nordic Lounge</strong> in <a data-udi="umb://document/7bd0ea2aff2942389cbf8acdba0a0e77" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7bd0ea2aff2942389cbf8acdba0a0e77}" title="Soldeu">Soldeu</a> is stylish and slick, sit back and relax to smooth music</li>
<li>Try <strong>Paddy's Bar</strong> in <a data-udi="umb://document/e86e0f4a587e4cd8be3c24d7da459a59" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e86e0f4a587e4cd8be3c24d7da459a59}" title="Pas de la Casa">Pas de la Casa</a> - as you guest it, an Irish bar, full of Irish charm</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/043e5aa9497c411db243e21ed0a5049b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/043e5aa9497c411db243e21ed0a5049b}" title="Andorra" class="c-btn">View Andorra</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
</div>
<div></div>
</div>
<div></div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2>Après Ski FAQ's:</h2>
<div>
<p><strong>What time does Après ski start?</strong> - You can of course stop for a lunch time tipple or enjoy a glass with your dinner, but the general rule is once you have finished skiing or snowboarding for the day or once the lifts have shut for that day.</p>
</div>
<p><strong>Where is the best place to go for Après Ski?</strong> - Europe is renowned for being the best place to visit if you want to enjoy Après ski to its fullest.</p>
</div>
<p><strong>Is music part of Après ski?</strong> - Of course, this is really the highlight, be it a nightclub, background pub music or live music filling the air.</p>
<div></div>
<p> </p>
<h2>Inspiration for Après Ski holidays</h2>
<p> </p>
<div class="col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Top 10 Après bars</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13070897/best-apres-ski-resorts-inghams-holidays-meribel.jpg" alt="apresski" data-udi="umb://media/3625ab68add640aeaafd6f8e44350959" /></p>
<p>We have devised a top 10 après ski bars list - here we let you know where we think the hottest venues in the Alps are located. We'll also tell you why to head to them to get your apr<span>è</span>s fix and what you can expect. Shine up those dancing shoes!</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/417504a232344dccb745012cf184d1f3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/417504a232344dccb745012cf184d1f3}" title="Insider's Guide: Top 10 Apres Ski Bars" class="c-btn" data-anchor="#">View Guide</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Top 6 Festivals</h3>
<p><img style="color: #000000; font-weight: 400;" src="/media/13070895/best-apres-ski-resorts-inghams-holidays.jpg" alt="skifestival" data-udi="umb://media/4b5acb0204d74d52950e503c183bdd6c" /></p>
<p><span>Festivals on the slopes -</span> Ranging from music to comedy to parties, these festivals are the places to be at winter and if you've not booked your ski holiday and tickets then now's as good a time as any! Enjoy the party life out on the slopes.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/d4475de1efce42b68ec9a9457877a290" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d4475de1efce42b68ec9a9457877a290}" title="Insider’s Guide: Our top 6 springtime ski festivals" class="c-btn">View Guide</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Travel with confidence </h2>
<p>When you choose an Inghams holiday, you can travel with confidence. We’re here to take the stress out of travelling. We’ve put extra measures in place for your peace of mind. We’ll help keep both you and your money safe.</p>
<p><img src="/media/13095389/inghams-in-safe-hands-charcoal.png" alt="safehands" data-udi="umb://media/afba17a916e84fcc848acce5dda4f9c4" /></p>
